ten auf mehr als nur menschliche Instanzen auf.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aFamiliensoziologie. 4aKonflikt. 4aMedien. 4aMediensoziologie. 4aMigration. 4aMikrosoziologie. 4aQualitative Sozialforschung. 4aSoziologie. 4aStreit. 4aTechnik. 4aTechniksoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aConflict.  aMedia.  aMicrosociology.  aMigration.  aQualitative Social Research.  aSociology of Family.  aSociology of Media.  aSociology of Technology.  aSociology.  aTechnology.40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839462447?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839462447423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839462447/original  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK